      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "READY MAREA (1) was on debut last start over 1050m at this track and after making a poor beginning recovered well to race third of 11 in behind the speed to the turn and then fought on well to score by a head. Trained here and in a fitter state should be hard to beat again. IT'SALL ABOUT MARY (2) debuted last start over 1000m at Eagle Farm and finished a well-beaten sixth of seven when, after making a poor beginning, she lost ground, then raced greenly when placed under pressure in the home straight. Dropping back to provincial grade and having had racing experience should improve on that last run. ANOTHER CHAMPERS (3) is a two-year-old filly on debut from the Stuart Kendrick stable. By Wild Ruler from Miss Clicquot. Placed second of four in a recent trial run over 1000m at Sunshine Coast Inner. Use the late betting market to get a better guide with regard to her chances. IRONROAD SPIRIT (6) is trained here and is making her debut run. Has placed in both trial runs and is in the mix.",
